'''''Master Miner''''' is a maze shooter for [[IBM PC compatible]]s  released as a [[self-booting disk]] by Funtastic in 1983. It was written  by [[Dan Illowsky]] who previously wrote ''[[Snack Attack]]'' for the [[Apple II series|Apple II]].<ref name=giantlist/> The game involves collecting diamonds while avoiding bandits.

